```plantuml
@startuml mebaysan_Modern-Data-Architecture
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Airbyte" as Airbyte #lightblue

rectangle "Python Script" as PythonScript #lightgreen

rectangle "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL #lightcoral

rectangle "DBT" as DBT #lightyellow

rectangle "Apache Superset" as Superset #lightsteelblue

rectangle "Docker Compose" as DockerCompose #lightgray

rectangle "Nginx" as Nginx #aliceblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> Airbyte : initiate data extraction
User --> PythonScript : execute alternative data load

' Data ingestion
Airbyte --> PostgreSQL : load data from CSV
PythonScript --> PostgreSQL : load data from CSV

' Data transformation and modeling
DBT --> PostgreSQL : transform and model data

' Data visualization
Superset --> PostgreSQL : query transformed data
User --> Superset : access visualizations

' Docker Compose orchestration
DockerCompose --> Airbyte : deploy container
DockerCompose --> PostgreSQL : deploy container
DockerCompose --> DBT : deploy container
DockerCompose --> Superset : deploy container
DockerCompose --> Nginx : deploy container

' Nginx reverse proxy
User --> Nginx : access pgAdmin
Nginx --> PostgreSQL : proxy requests to pgAdmin

@enduml
```